sequenceDiagram
    participant P as TransactionMQProducer
    participant B as SendMessageProcessor
    participant T as TransactionalMessageService
    participant E as EndTransactionProcessor
    participant C as TransactionalMessageCheckService
    participant L as Producer TransactionListener

    P->>B: 发送 Transaction Prepared 消息
    B->>T: asyncPrepareMessage
    T-->>P: Half Message 写入成功

    P->>L: executeLocalTransaction
    alt Commit
        P->>E: END_TRANSACTION(COMMIT)
        E->>T: commitMessage
        E->>E: 恢复真实 Topic 并写最终消息
        E->>T: deletePrepareMessage
    else Rollback
        P->>E: END_TRANSACTION(ROLLBACK)
        E->>T: rollbackMessage
        E->>T: deletePrepareMessage
    else Unknown或无响应
        C->>T: check(timeout, max)
        T->>L: Broker 回查 Producer
        L->>E: 返回 Commit / Rollback / Unknown
    end
